1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
My name is Praveen, and I am 40 years old

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,000
I work in IT

3
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:14,000
While working on the computer a lot, I got a lot of shoulder and neck pain

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,000
For 3-4 weeks, it became a hassle and hurt a lot

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:30,000
I got checked in a hospital, and they gave me painkillers. I used it for 2 weeks.
It relieved the pain, but if I didn't take the tablets, the pain started again

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:42,000
The doctor never told me about physical therapy, but I had hope
it'd make my condition even a little bit better

7
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:50,000
The doctor finally suggested it, and I came to NRI Seva

8
00:00:50,000 --> 00:01:00,000
After a while, sir and madam told me to get an X-ray, so I went out and got an X-ray
so I could be properly analyzed

9
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:19,000
I showed them where the pain was, they analyzed the x-ray,
and started me on treatments for my neck and shoulder

10
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:35,000
They gave me a sandbag for support for my shoulder.
I couldn't even carry that one-kilo bag

11
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:54,000
I even requested saying it was very heavy. But the past 3-4 days
the bag wasn't heavy anymore because of the treatment

12
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:08,000
After almost two weeks of treatment, my current condition
is 95% better than my original condition